title: Behavioral Health Professional Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 1 week. I interviewed at Casa (Portland, ME)
Interview Descriptions: The process was rather quick and straight forward. Typical interview questions with nothing out of the ordinary being asked. I knew the results immediately after my interview. I was asked to supply a copy of my college degree and other documents. It took sometime to begin working since you have to also interview with each client.
Interview Questions: Where do you see yourself in 5 years?
